<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>스윙 스캔 메일 구독</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      background: #f3f5fb;
      color: #1f2937;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Malgun Gothic", sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .subscribe-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      padding: 32px;
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 100%;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
    }
    .subscribe-card h1 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .subscribe-card .lead {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .btn-brand {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      color: #fff;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .btn-brand:hover { color: #fff; opacity: 0.92; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="subscribe-card">
    <h1><i class="bi bi-envelope-paper-heart me-2"></i>스윙 스캔 메일 구독</h1>
    <div class="lead">
      매 평일 <strong>22:00 KST</strong> 에 그날의 스윙 스캔 결과 (상위 15종목, 점수·매수가·시장 컨텍스트) 를
      이메일로 받아보세요. 휴장일에는 발송되지 않습니다.
    </div>

    <% if (message) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-success small"><i class="bi bi-check-circle me-1"></i><%= message %></div>
    <% } %>
    <% if (error) { %>
      <div class="alert alert-danger small"><i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle me-1"></i><%= error %></div>
    <% } %>

    <form method="post" action="/subscribe">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label class="form-label small fw-semibold">이메일</label>
        <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control" placeholder="you@example.com" required autocomplete="email" />
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-brand w-100">
        <i class="bi bi-envelope-check me-1"></i>구독 시작
      </button>
    </form>

    <div class="text-secondary small mt-4" style="font-size: 0.78rem;">
      ※ 구독 정보는 본 서버의 <code>.subscribers.json</code> 에만 저장됩니다.
      구독 취소는 메일 하단의 "구독 취소" 링크로 즉시 가능합니다.
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3 mt-4 pt-3 border-top small">
      <a href="/" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary">
        <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-1"></i>딥다이브로
      </a>
      <a href="/scan" class="text-decoration-none text-secondary">
        <i class="bi bi-radar me-1"></i>단타 스캔
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
